ovided a sentence's worth of story and an obscene amount of jokes/refrences that fell flat at their best, and were irritating at their worst. Dictiny's sense of humor does not go beyond ""HEY!!!! Remeber THIS thing??? LOL. OMG SO RANDOM, am I rite???XD"". I'm talking Schwarzenegger and LotR. The skimming the surface level of muck from over exposed culture.So as it stands with it's current proformance issues, simplistic hybrid gameplay, and obnoxious writing, I'd actually recomend it at its current early access price of 75% off. Who knows, the gameplay may evolve to such a fantastic level that even a horrendous sense of humor wont bring it down. Or, maybe the writing will improve, but that honestly seems much less likely as Dicetiny's identy seems pretty concrete. There's some real potential here and I'd hate to see it go to waste by the Dev's limiting their creativity and adhering only to existing ip's or out dated refrences."
